  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A soft but immutable heartbeat resonates through your skull when you wear this helmet. <span class=\"name name-fuel\">A T L A S</span>.<br>The pulse is strangely soothing.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>戴上这顶头盔，你的头骨能够感觉到一种柔软却又无比清晰的心跳共鸣。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">阿、特、拉、斯</span>。<br>虽然无法解释，但那种脉搏让人无比平静。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>戴上這頂頭盔時，一陣溫柔又規律的心跳聲在你的頭骨中迴盪。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">寰 宇</span>。<br>這股脈動充滿莫名的療癒之力。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
